188
00:09:37,680 --> 00:09:39,080
Just knowing you're wrong isn't enough.

189
00:09:39,280 --> 00:09:40,240
You have to change.

190
00:09:40,880 --> 00:09:42,160
You have to work harder.

191
00:09:42,440 --> 00:09:43,800
Learn from shame, then rise to the challenge.

192
00:09:44,560 --> 00:09:46,480
Yes, you're absolutely right.

193
00:09:46,840 --> 00:09:47,640
