194
00:09:48,680 --> 00:09:49,520
Okay.

195
00:09:56,360 --> 00:09:57,160
Lao Man.

196
00:09:57,560 --> 00:09:58,360
What?

197
00:09:59,640 --> 00:10:01,280
Chengxintang paper is being recreated.

198
00:10:02,280 --> 00:10:03,280
