202
00:10:10,000 --> 00:10:11,160
I'll wait for your good news.

203
00:10:14,040 --> 00:10:17,080
"Silent, alone, I climb the western tower..."

204
00:10:17,800 --> 00:10:18,840
Director Liao, Director Liao!

205
00:10:19,120 --> 00:10:20,760
Don't go climbing any tower.

206
00:10:20,760 --> 00:10:22,240
Hurry up and tell us what happened.

207
00:10:22,240 --> 00:10:22,840
Yeah.

208
00:10:22,840 --> 00:10:24,240
