211
00:10:50,200 --> 00:10:51,920
Not a single flaw.

212
00:10:52,840 --> 00:10:55,240
A sight that soothes the soul.

213
00:10:56,080 --> 00:10:56,960
Lao Xuan.

214
00:10:57,560 --> 00:10:59,520
After a lifetime of scooping paper,

215
00:10:59,560 --> 00:11:02,320
I finally get to see Chengxintang paper myself.

216
00:11:03,080 --> 00:11:03,880
It's all worth it.

217
00:11:04,800 --> 00:11:06,360
In *Dongpo Zhilin*,

218
00:11:06,680 --> 00:11:08,720
there's a quote from Su Shi:

219
00:11:11,400 --> 00:11:14,760
"Lord Li's Chengxintang paper

220
00:11:15,720 --> 00:11:18,200
no longer exists in this world."

221
00:11:19,320 --> 00:11:20,800
And in that same era, Ouyang Xiu

222
00:11:21,040 --> 00:11:24,200
once gifted two sheets of Chengxintang paper

223
00:11:24,640 --> 00:11:26,520
to the great calligrapher Cai Xiang.

224
00:11:27,320 --> 00:11:30,400
Cai Xiang was so overjoyed he couldn't sleep.

225
00:11:30,760 --> 00:11:32,280
He described the paper as:

226
00:11:33,080 --> 00:11:34,720
"Skin like an eggshell membrane,

227
00:11:34,880 --> 00:11:36,600
firm and pure like jade,

228
00:11:37,400 --> 00:11:38,880
smooth as spring ice,

229
00:11:39,200 --> 00:11:41,880
fine and dense like a cocoon."

230
00:11:42,520 --> 00:11:43,480
The real question is,

231
00:11:43,920 --> 00:11:45,280
such precious paper,

232
00:11:45,600 --> 00:11:47,560
how did Ouyang Xiu get his hands on it?

233
00:11:47,720 --> 00:11:50,240
There's a story behind that too.

234
00:11:50,560 --> 00:11:54,040
Yangzhou governor Liu Chang went to Jinling,

235
00:11:54,400 --> 00:11:58,960
and was lucky to obtain Li Yu's relics,

236
00:11:59,360 --> 00:12:02,040
over a hundred sheets of Chengxintang paper.

237
00:12:02,400 --> 00:12:06,360
Liu Chang gave ten sheets to Ouyang Xiu.

238
00:12:06,480 --> 00:12:09,480
Back then, Ouyang Xiu was in a high position.

239
00:12:09,480 --> 00:12:11,280
Liu Chang was sucking up to his superior.

240
00:12:11,720 --> 00:12:12,600
That's understandable.

241
00:12:13,120 --> 00:12:14,120
Uncle Xuan,

242
00:12:14,280 --> 00:12:16,120
