243
00:12:16,360 --> 00:12:19,160
This paper, a four-foot square,

244
00:12:19,560 --> 00:12:20,520
weighs five grams.

245
00:12:20,960 --> 00:12:21,800
Five grams?

246
00:12:22,200 --> 00:12:23,280
So by that math,

247
00:12:24,080 --> 00:12:25,280
a ream of four-foot sheets

248
00:12:25,680 --> 00:12:26,840
weighs only two jin.

249
00:12:28,200 --> 00:12:29,360
Oh my goodness.

250
00:12:29,960 --> 00:12:32,840
Our regular four-foot ream

251
00:12:32,840 --> 00:12:34,280
weighs about five jin.

252
00:12:34,720 --> 00:12:36,320
That's a huge difference.

253
00:12:37,120 --> 00:12:40,120
That's why replicating it is so hard.

254
00:12:41,760 --> 00:12:44,160
Now you get what I mean, right?

255
00:12:45,200 --> 00:12:48,040
You two, seize this topic.

256
00:12:48,280 --> 00:12:50,320
