258
00:12:52,480 --> 00:12:56,960
Cover the whole process of replicating Chengxintang paper.

259
00:12:56,960 --> 00:12:59,400
Our video channel will blow up for sure!

260
00:13:01,000 --> 00:13:01,760
That's great!

261
00:13:02,080 --> 00:13:02,920
What's so great about it?

262
00:13:03,320 --> 00:13:04,480
Get in the zone, start filming!

263
00:13:07,280 --> 00:13:08,120
Lao Xuan,

264
00:13:08,760 --> 00:13:10,800
I know that just mentioning Hongxing Factory

265
00:13:11,440 --> 00:13:13,000
