271
00:13:27,200 --> 00:13:28,840
The requirements of that order

272
00:13:29,640 --> 00:13:32,920
are very close to Chengxintang paper.

273
00:13:33,160 --> 00:13:35,280
Our tech department worked over a month,

274
00:13:35,600 --> 00:13:36,640
