275
00:13:36,800 --> 00:13:40,000
I heard you're developing Chengxintang paper.

276
00:13:40,360 --> 00:13:41,800
The chairman's idea

277
00:13:42,200 --> 00:13:44,880
was to have me talk with you first,

278
00:13:45,280 --> 00:13:46,360
to see if it's possible

279
00:13:46,360 --> 00:13:49,240
for our two firms to co-develop it,

280
00:13:49,680 --> 00:13:52,200
and make a co-branded paper.

281
00:13:52,880 --> 00:13:54,200
Both professionally and personally,

282
00:13:54,600 --> 00:13:58,400
